        public Division(java.lang.String b,
                java.lang.String e,
                java.lang.String id,
                int l,
                int nri,
                boolean b1)
        builds a division
        Parameters:
        b - a string: the id of the first graphical unit
        e - a string: the id of the last graphical unit
        id - a string: the unique id of the division
        l - an integer: the level of the division
        nri - an integer:the internal number
        b1 - : true if the division was created automatically
